<h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>

<p>Hi <%= firstName %>,</p>

<p>
  Welcome to <strong>ProFile AI</strong>. Please use the code below to verify
  your email address and activate your account so you can start building
  AI-powered, ATS-optimized resumes.
</p>

<div class="otp-box">
  <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
  <div class="otp-timer">⏱ This code expires in <%= expiryMinutes %> minutes</div>
</div>

<p class="muted">
  If you did not create a ProFile AI account, you can safely ignore this
  email — no further action is required.
</p>
